      • configureAsSMS

        public void configureAsSMS(java.lang.String countryCode,
                           java.lang.String phoneNumber,
                           java.lang.String username,
                           java.lang.String message)
        Configures the receiver as AylaNotificationTypeSMS for the specified parameters. This is an alternative method instead of using AylaContact.
        参数:
        countryCode -
        phoneNumber - The phone number
        username - The username of the app
        message - The message of the SMS

      • configureAsEmail

        public void configureAsEmail(AylaContact contact,
                             java.lang.String message,
                             java.lang.String username,
                             AylaEmailTemplate emailTemplate)
        Configures the receiver as AylaNotificationTypeEmail for the specified AylaContact with the specified message and AylaEmailTemplate
        参数:
        contact - The AylaContact that will receive the app
        message - The message of the email
        username - The username of the app
        emailTemplate - An AylaEmailTemplate with the email specifications

      • configureAsPushAndroid

        public void configureAsPushAndroid(java.lang.String registrationId,
                                   java.lang.String message,
                                   java.lang.String pushSound,
                                   java.lang.String pushMetaData)
        Configures the receiver as AylaNotificationType for Google Push
        参数:
        registrationId - The registration ID needed for GCM
        message - The Push message for GCM
        pushSound - The sound file name present on mobile app eg: my_sound_file.mp3
        pushMetaData - Comma separated data needed by app eg: {"key1":"value1", "key2":"value2"}

      • configureAsPushFCM

        public void configureAsPushFCM(java.lang.String registrationId,
                               java.lang.String message,
                               java.lang.String pushSound,
                               java.lang.String pushMetaData)
        Configures the receiver as AylaNotificationType for FCM Push
        参数:
        registrationId - The registration ID needed for FCM
        message - The Push message for FCM
        pushSound - The sound file name present on mobile app eg: my_sound_file.mp3
        pushMetaData - Comma separated data needed by app eg: {"key1":"value1", "key2":"value2"}

      • configureAsPushBaidu

        public void configureAsPushBaidu(java.lang.String applicationId,
                                 java.lang.String channelId,
                                 java.lang.String message,
                                 java.lang.String pushSound,
                                 java.lang.String pushMetaData)
        Configures the receiver as AylaNotificationType for Baidu
        参数:
        applicationId - The Application ID
        channelId - The Channel ID
        message - The Push Message
        pushSound - The sound the Phone should emit on receiving this Notification
        pushMetaData - The optional Meta Data to be included in the message
